{"title": "dmesg", "source": "gtfobins", "source_label": "GTFOBins", "path": "dmesg", "html": "<h1>dmesg</h1>\n<h2>File Read</h2>\n<pre><code class=\"language-bash\">dmesg -rF /path/to/input-file</code></pre>\n<h2>Inherit</h2>\n<pre><code class=\"language-bash\">dmesg -H</code></pre>", "excerpt": "dmesg File Read dmesg -rF /path/to/input-file Inherit dmesg -H", "tags": ["func:file-read", "func:inherit", "ctx:sudo", "ctx:suid", "ctx:unprivileged"]}